What you need to know:  Through partnership with Ligue 1 side Olympique Lyon, the academy targets players who were born between 2008 and 2010 for exchange programmes with the French clubThe academy has provided a website link for talented footballers across the country to apply free of charge to join themRegional balance will be considered as selectors pick 22 boys and 22 girls who will be trained with a view of joining the paid ranks abroad